      <title>印度 CCI 批准 Mankind Pharma 收购疫苗制造商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/india-s-cci-approves-mankind-pharma-s-purchase-of-vaccine-maker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据印度竞争委员会发布的消息，印度反垄断监管机构批准 Mankind Pharma Ltd. 以 1363 亿卢比（16 亿美元）收购疫苗制造商 Bharat Serums and Vaccines Ltd.。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/india-s-cci-approves-mankind-pharma-s-purchase-of-vaccine-maker</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:33:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
